#####################
# Solution

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_SOLUTION
${PAR}SOLUTION:$PAR
Each derivative just adds a multiple of \( i\xi \).  So
$BR
$BR
\(
\displaystyle
\mathcal{F}[f'''(x)] = 
-i\xi^3
 \hat{f}(\xi) \)
$BR
$BR
\(
\displaystyle
\mathcal{F}[f^{(4)}(x)] = 
\xi^4
\hat{f}(\xi) \)
$BR
$BR
\(
\displaystyle
\mathcal{F}[$a f(x) + $b f'(x) + $c f''(x)]
= ( $a + $b i \xi - $c \xi^2 ) \hat{f}(\xi) \)
END_SOLUTION
Context()->normalStrings;

